latestPosts.caption:
1st Emirati to Win 👑🇦🇪

Final Crowning Moment for Miss UAE!!! 🇦🇪👑 

1st Time in History of beauty pageant World!!! 

I Am so Honored To Be the 1st Emirati Woman to Win an International Beauty Pageant !! @missplanetinternational 
 

As the first Emirati woman to win an international beauty pageant and claim the title of Miss Planet International 2024, I feel incredibly honored and humbled. It’s a moment of pride, not just for me, but for my country and everyone who shares the vision of a more sustainable and inclusive future.

Winning this crown signifies the power of perseverance, the importance of standing for a cause, and the potential to inspire others. It’s a platform for me to amplify my mission of promoting environmental sustainability, empowering women, and ensuring that every child has access to education. This achievement isn’t just mine—it belongs to everyone who believes in change, innovation, and the drive to make the world a better place.

I am filled with gratitude, knowing that this is only the beginning of a journey where actions speak louder than words, and I can leave a legacy of impact and hope for generations to come.✨

Wearing a beautifully Customized dress from @michaelcinco5 @michael5inco @sayed5inco 🔥🔥🔥✨
